Suzanne Storrs https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suzanne_Storrs 0 Suzanne Storrs (April 13, 1934 – January 25, 1995), born Suzanne Storrs Poulton, was a former Miss Utah and an American television actress who appeared in sixteen different television series between 1954 and 1961, usually as the beautiful leading lady.
